item.title: FNMA
item.description: score:-39 Chances: Fannie Mae has received the 2024 ENERGY STAR Partner of the Year award for its outstanding contributions to increasing adoption of energy-efficiency improvements in housing for the 10th consecutive year. The company has announced the winning bidder for its twenty-third Community Impact Pool of non-performing loans, showing its proactive approach to managing its loan portfolio.
